{"tid":1863421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(鬼拍後尾枕)九龍灣防暴狗：你估我好想著咩 引起恐慌㗎","createTime":"2020-02-05T06:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T07:40:20.000Z","uid":5416,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0593106ef82a6b026dbb3e377e5243f63c0f3244","tid":1863421,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"【九龍灣排口罩出防暴 防暴：你估好想著咩 引起恐慌㗎】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣有商店出售口罩，超過5000名市民排隊，更引來防暴警員到場維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者上前詢問為何要出動防暴，有警員回應，由於人數眾多，臨時被抽調到場。對於身上裝束更笑言：「你估我好想著咩，引起恐慌㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=165246748225066&amp;id=109301110486297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D165246748225066%26id%3D109301110486297&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=165a69b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=165246748225066&amp;id=109301110486297</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你哋出現已經引起恐慌 <br />\n<br />\n你哋會唔會諗多咗"},{"pid":"0d575a9a27a7911113cf25e22e36be49d7bb2261","tid":1863421,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb3d83a79519d2a5a2e5dfd46046b8a57aa1c7b7","tid":1863421,"uid":159876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"佢地原來知會引起恐慌。。"},{"pid":"7c7d889a6fee813fabf7c6fdadaf2d4e2e2b7eee","tid":1863421,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600201c742837d30bafa026918e18a56a349a114","tid":1863421,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"佢地就係要恐嚇市民"},{"pid":"a2df6d774b670c557cd19e6e344140926ad79d8e","tid":1863421,"uid":30506,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:02:27.000Z","msg":"白警<img src=\"/assets/fac